mxCell.value: Once you have a forge you'll be able to smelt iron for tools and nails and such. Until you can mine iron though all iron comes from salvage from the old battleground.
The start of Act-1-2 is triggered by missions getting unlocked. You will have one minion, and they're only able to forage. You can only make baskets and meditate.

Once all of the Act 1 tasks have been finished Act 2 starts with an attack by kobolds from the caverns below. Your minions may all survive if you have equipped them well. The attack reveals a series of caverns under the keep.
Need to figure out when all of this happens, but these events are all part of the critical path. They'll probably all happen sometime in act 2 though.
These foraging events are planned for, but they're not yet in the game. I don't think they'll effect the stage at all though.
Not sure yet what triggers adding these projects.
